# Changelog


### Added
- Initial release of the CLI API testing tool.
- Support for CRUD operations (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE).
- Ability to save API response data to a JSON file.
- Command-line interface for executing API requests.

### Changed
- Improved error handling for HTTP requests.
- Enhanced command-line argument parsing.

### Fixed
- Fixed JSON parsing issues with command-line input.
- Resolved syntax errors in the script.

## [1.0.0] - 2025-12-01

### Added
- Basic functionality for making HTTP requests using axios.
- Command-line argument support for specifying HTTP method, URL, and data.
- Output file option to save API responses.


## [0.1.0] - 2024-12-30

### Added
- Project initialization with basic CLI setup.


